\begin_layout Standard
为了给指数映射提供一个更通用的定义，让我们定义切增量 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\tau}\triangleq\mathbf{v}t\in\mathbb{R}^{m}$
\end_inset

 作为每一时刻的速度，这样我们就有 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}=\mathbf{v}^{\wedge}t\in\mathfrak{g}$
\end_inset

 做为李代数中的一个点。指数映射和它的逆(对数映射)，现在可以写成，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\exp & :\mathfrak{g}\rightarrow\mathcal{M}\quad;\quad\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\mapsto\mathcal{X}=\exp\left(\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\right)\label{eq:14}\\
\log: & \mathcal{M}\rightarrow\mathfrak{g}\quad;\quad\mathcal{X}\mapsto\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}=\log(\mathcal{X}).\label{eq:15}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
通过写出绝对收敛的泰勒级数，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\exp\left(\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\right)=\mathcal{E}+\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}+\frac{1}{2}\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge2}+\frac{1}{3!}\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge3}+\cdots,\label{eq:16}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

并且利用 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}$
\end_inset

 的幂的代数性质，得到了乘法群中的指数封闭形式。然后将这些求逆以找到对数映射。指数映射的关键性质是
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\exp\left(\left(t+s\right)\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\right) & =\exp\left(t\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\right)\exp\left(s\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\right)\label{eq:17}\\
\exp\left(t\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\right) & =\exp\left(\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\right)^{t}\label{eq:18}\\
\exp\left(-\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\right) & =\exp\left(\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\right)^{-1}\label{eq:19}\\
\exp\left(\mathcal{X}\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\mathcal{X}^{-1}\right) & =\mathcal{X}\exp\left(\boldsymbol{\tau}^{\wedge}\right)\mathcal{X}^{-1}\label{eq:20}
\end{align}

\end_inset

