\end_inset

 我们用方程 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:41a"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 定义
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\mathbf{J}_{\mathcal{X}}^{\mathcal{X}\cdot v} & \triangleq\frac{^{\mathcal{X}}D\mathcal{X}\cdot v}{D\mathcal{X}}\label{eq:77}\\
\mathbf{J}_{v}^{\mathcal{X}\cdot v} & \triangleq\frac{^{v}D\mathcal{X}\cdot v}{Dv}.\label{eq:78}
\end{align}

