\begin_layout Proof
如前所述，
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{Ad}_{g}(Y)=gYg^{-1}$
\end_inset

，并且有
\begin_inset Formula $g=e^{tX}$
\end_inset

，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{Ad}_{e^{tX}}(Y)=e^{tX}Ye^{-tX}.
\]

\end_inset

取其在
\begin_inset Formula $t=0$
\end_inset

处的导数，我们有：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left.\frac{d}{dt}\left(e^{tX}Ye^{-tX}\right)\right|_{t=0} & =\left.\frac{d}{dt}(\exp(tX)\cdot Y)\cdot\exp(-tX)+\exp(tX)\cdot Y\cdot\frac{d}{dt}\exp(-tX)\right|_{t=0}\\
 & =\left.X\exp(tX)\cdot Y\cdot\exp(-tX)-\exp(tX)\cdot Y\cdot X\exp(-tX)\right|_{t=0}\\
 & =XY-YX\\
 & =[X,Y]\\
 & =\mathrm{ad}_{X}Y,
\end{align*}

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{Ad}_{e^{X}}=e^{\mathrm{ad}_{X}}.
\]

\end_inset


