，我们有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
D_{\log}(\boldsymbol{\omega}) & =\mathbf{J}_{l}{}^{-1}\left(\boldsymbol{\omega}\right)\\
 & =\mathbf{I}-\frac{1}{2}\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\times}+\left(\frac{1}{\theta^{2}}-\frac{1+\cos\theta}{2\theta\sin\theta}\right)\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\times}^{2}
